In 2012, the '''Margaret Clark Prize''' for Victoria University of Wellington honours politics students was established in her name.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.fis.org.nz/BreakOut/vuw/schols.phtml?prize+600316 | title=Margaret Clark Prize | publisher=Victoria University of Wellington | accessdate=18 July 2014}}</ref>
